@node Main "MLink - Documentation"

                               MLink 1.12

                       Created by Charles-N. Jacob

  @{" MLink " link play} is based on the well known puzzle where you try to recreate
four coloured chains, one in each column in the least amount of moves.
Unlike the real game, MLink's four sides are 'flattened' on a 4 x 4 game
board, but it is played just like the original game.

  As with all my Workbench games, its window is resizeable and the game
board is redisplayed according to the new window size.

  Have fun!

             @{" Install and Play the game " link play}
             @{"   Features of the game    " link features}
             @{"         History           " link histo}
             @{"       Legal stuff         " link legal}
